{"tid":2181762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"小行星9月2日飛過地球 最近距離12萬km","createTime":"2020-08-30T21:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T23:22:41.000Z","uid":285559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"684ff8ff28ad947cad1c0a96252601f00aefd36d","tid":2181762,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T21:29:39.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國國家航空暨太空總署 （NASA）公開數據顯示，1顆直徑為22公尺至49公尺的「近地小行星」即將在台灣時間9月2日0時12分，以三分之一地月距離與地球擦肩而過。<br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署數據顯示，「2011 ES4」小行星將在台灣時間9月2日0時12分，以秒速8.16公里的速度與地球擦肩而過，最近距離預估為12萬1301公里，比地球與月球距離（38萬4472.3公里）的三分之一更近，NASA模擬中，並未顯示該小行星與地球在未來有碰撞的可能性，因此沒有潛在危險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3276426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3276426&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=983fff42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3276426&h=6a8604bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3276426</a>"},{"pid":"3b616c273885a67c6f4fda5313f77f06238db65a","tid":2181762,"uid":218063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T21:54:44.000Z","msg":"2020話唔埋"},{"pid":"29ef8afc9501b19cc8871cc2e38c376b9ff664bd","tid":2181762,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T22:00:21.000Z","msg":"話唔定好似磁石咁突然間吸過黎呢"},{"pid":"2eb1ef4b2cd9fcbb2aa2948e622b12e9cca2b0f0","tid":2181762,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T23:19:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ae9c0404d14dbfc5b4bb8c92084869652e8ea82","tid":2181762,"uid":172627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T23:22:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VzF-Q8qIG-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVzF-Q8qIG-4&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoBYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=847113c1\" target=